    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Here&rsquo;s my quick and dirty cheat sheet for using the Octopress blogging framework.</p>

<h3>Command Line</h3>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>rake new_post["Post title here"]
</span><span class='line'>rake generate
</span><span class='line'>rake deploy
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>Markdown Syntax</h3>

<h4>Headers</h4>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='Clojure'><span class='line'><span class="o">#</span> <span class="nv">This</span> <span class="nv">is</span> <span class="nv">an</span> <span class="nv">&lt;h1&gt;</span> <span class="nv">tag</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">##</span> <span class="nv">This</span> <span class="nv">is</span> <span class="nv">an</span> <span class="nv">&lt;h2&gt;</span> <span class="nv">tag</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="o">######</span> <span class="nv">This</span> <span class="nv">is</span> <span class="nv">an</span> <span class="nv">&lt;h6&gt;</span> <span class="nv">tag</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Emphasis</h4>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='Clojure'><span class='line'><span class="nv">*This</span> <span class="nv">text</span> <span class="nv">will</span> <span class="nv">be</span> <span class="nv">italic*</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">_This</span> <span class="nv">will</span> <span class="nv">also</span> <span class="nv">be</span> <span class="nv">italic_</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">**This</span> <span class="nv">text</span> <span class="nv">will</span> <span class="nv">be</span> <span class="nv">bold**</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">__This</span> <span class="nv">will</span> <span class="nv">also</span> <span class="nv">be</span> <span class="nv">bold__</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nv">*You</span> <span class="nv">**can**</span> <span class="nv">combine</span> <span class="nv">them*</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Unordered Lists</h4>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='Clojure'><span class='line'><span class="nb">* </span><span class="nv">Item</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nb">* </span><span class="nv">Item</span> <span class="mi">2</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nb">* </span><span class="nv">Item</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="nv">a</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nb">* </span><span class="nv">Item</span> <span class="mi">2</span><span class="nv">b</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h4>Ordered Lists</h4>

